{"tid":2244114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曼谷緊急狀態禁止集會 ，泰國民：最衰都係黃屍！","createTime":"2020-10-15T08:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T06:53:18.000Z","uid":219635,"like":161,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2a87b75ad2a42f30a310aae449823c64ae652b","tid":2244114,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"「經濟日報」泰國曼谷的反政府示威有新發展，泰國政府指示威者的行動引起混亂、阻塞交通，今晨宣布曼谷進入緊急狀態，禁止進行5人以上的集會。警方對政府大樓附近的集會進行清場，3名關鍵示威領袖被捕。<br />\n<br />\n泰國總理巴育（Prayuth Chan-ocha）周四清晨頒布緊急狀態令，除了禁止大型集會，傳媒報道亦受限，禁止作出會引起恐懼、刻意扭曲資訊、誤導，危害國家安全的報道，當局並有權禁止民眾進入任何區域。<br />\n<br />\n泰國多個團體周三發起示威，要求總理巴育下台以及限制國王的權力。他們先在曼谷民主紀念碑集會，後來突破警方防綫，遊行至總理府外示威，及至午夜，示威人群仍未散去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2777575/【泰國示威】曼谷緊急狀態禁止集會%20多名示威領袖被捕（多圖）?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2777575%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BC%E8%B0%B7%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%2520%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96%EF%BC%89%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=6235fbf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2777575/【泰國示威】曼谷緊急狀態禁止集會%20多名示威領袖被捕（多圖）?mtc=20023</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">以下為支持皇室穿著黃色衣服的支持者圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ra2JpNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRa2JpNx.png&h=6e7a8ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zHM609.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zHM609.png&h=9c7ea70d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11LV0mw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11LV0mw.png&h=023dbcfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXogKOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXogKOt.png&h=7ca4e12f&s={SI